<!-- ══════════════════ FAQ ══════════════════ -->
<div id="faq" class="section-bg-white">
    <div class="section reveal">
        <div class="section-eyebrow">FAQ</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">Common questions</h2>

        <div class="faq-list">
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question" data-faq-toggle>
                    Is the free plan actually free — no trial?
                    <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">Yes. The Free plan is free forever — no credit card required, no trial period,
                    no expiry. You get 3 team members, 1 shared inbox, and 10 GB storage at no cost, for as long as you
                    want.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question" data-faq-toggle>
                    How does flat pricing work — what if my team grows?
                    <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">Unlike per-seat tools, we don't charge per user. Each plan has a maximum team
                    size (e.g. 20 members on Silver). When you need more, just upgrade to the next tier — one flat fee,
                    no per-user surprises.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question" data-faq-toggle>
                    How do I connect WhatsApp?
                    <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">WhatsApp integration is available on all paid plans. Connect your WhatsApp
                    Business number directly from the settings panel. Incoming messages appear alongside your emails in
                    the shared inbox.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question" data-faq-toggle>
                    Can I migrate from my current tool?
                    <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">Yes. You can connect your existing email accounts immediately. We're building a
                    full migration tool for conversation history — in the meantime, our support team can help guide you
                    through the process.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question" data-faq-toggle>
                    Is my data secure?
                    <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">All data is encrypted in transit and at rest. We follow industry-standard
                    security practices and are pursuing SOC 2 compliance. Your team's conversations and customer data
                    stay private.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question" data-faq-toggle>
                    Can I cancel anytime?
                    <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">Absolutely. No long-term contracts. Cancel anytime from your account settings
                    and you'll retain access until the end of your billing period.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>